  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But what the Germans did, when we find out what they did to people and the partisan come to told us and what they did to the people, what they took the kids, pregnant woman, the Ukrainian militia and the Germans militia.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They took kids, and they cut the veins in the pails, the plastic pails, blood.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Kids, babies.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Is not to describe what these animals did, particular was Hungarian, all Slavish, you know, units, Gestapo.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They are worse like the Germans.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "In our town, he told me-- [INAUDIBLE] told me in our town was just eight Germans.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Every day they ask for six virgin girls-- I'm sorry, eight virgin girls, so many minx coats, and so much gold delivered.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "When everything is finished, no more virgins, no more gold, then they bury them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "They dig their own holes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "One survivor ran away is my uncle, my mother's brother.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "He told me the whole story.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "He died in Israel.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I got him off in a [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Then, you know, I mix it up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I wanted everything to be-- and another thing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Stalin give orders after war in Berlin.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "We got in flyers, each one-- not flyers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "They give us letters, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "If you're looking for family to write to Stalin.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Really, Stalin doesn't, you know but--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There's the name was to write to Stalin.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So what I want to say in Katowice, they brought me my mother's brother, [?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Benny ?] Girszlak with a little machine, [INAUDIBLE] machine.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He used to make caps.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Two KGB guys to sign it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] in Katowice, you know, the street what I lived, what the government paid for me and civil clothes on account the Polish terrorist, you know, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
